	   _US-IRAQ-PROTEST GROUP _ U.S. government threatens fine for
breaking embargo.
	   BRUSSELS, Belgium _ Europe's dream of monetary union becomes
reality Thursday when 11 nations irrevocably lock their currencies
together to form the euro and create an economic giant. THE EURO.
Has moved. Will be updated after meeting starts at 1130 GMT. By
Paul Ames. AP Photo BRU101, TOK104, FRA105, ROM102, PAR105, LON112.
