	   _EURO-Q-AND-A, EURO COUNTRIES.
	   WASHINGTON _ Technology deals with China, including use of
Chinese missiles to launch U.S. satellites, have harmed national
security, a House committee concludes unanimously in a report
critical of dealings over two decades. US-CONGRESS-CHINA. Recap
with new material expected by 1000 GMT. By Will Lester. AP Photos
WX102-103.
	   PHNOM PENH, Cambodia _ As two Khmer Rouge leaders leave the
capital Thursday for a seaside vacation, the U.N. human rights
