Gold in Hong Kong closes higher
</HEADLINE>

<TEXT>
	   HONG KONG (AP) _ Gold in Hong Kong closed at U.S. dlrs 287.65 an
ounce on Thursday, up 70 U.S. cents from Wednesday's close of U.S.
dlrs 286.95.
