EURO LAUNCH:
----
BRUSSELS: EURO WRAP - The European Commission has agreed on the
irreversible rates at which the currencies of 11 EU nations will be
locked to form a new single currency. We have soundbites from
Jacques Santer, EU Commission President as well as European Central
Bank chief Wim Duisenberg. This will also include the official
signing ceremony.  (Expected First run Europe Update 1310 )
