BEL104-105.
	   ADEN, Yemen _ The luggage carried into the elevator of an Aden
hotel was enough to remind Laurence Whitehouse of the fear and the
death. ``That's my wife's,'' the tearful British teacher said,
pointing to one bag. His wife, Margaret, was one of four hostages
