u i &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-Iraq Advisory   12-31 0048
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-Iraq, Advisory,0048 </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
EDITORS:
</HEADLINE>

<TEXT>
	   Note that the latest Iraq lead, BC-Iraq, 2nd Ld-Writethru, made
an important clarification. Tariq Aziz did not specifically mention
the ``no-fly'' zones in saying Iraq would not ease its ``battle
against aggression.''
	   The AP
</TEXT>
